Contents
1) Download files from hitran website
2) Copy them to /home/sergio/SPECTRA/Global_Data_HITRAN2024/
3) make super-uper program TIPS_2024_try_include1.f
4) make main program that calls TIPS_2024
5) compile main program that calls TIPS_2024
6) Copy the Readme file to UMBC_LBL

TIPS2024 : ifort -o TIPS_2024_allisotopes.x -names uppercase -extend-source 132 -O3 TIPS_2024_allisotopes.f

