5) compile main program that calls TIPS_2024
--------------------------------------------------

Run
  compile_files.sc

which essentiallydoes
  ifort -o TIPS_2024_allisotopes.x -names uppercase -extend-source 132 -O3 TIPS_2024_allisotopes.f

